Trainee to be involved in (not limited to):
• Bookkeeping and invoicing processes
• Build, check, and expand client database and key contact
information
• Working with the director on the branding of the company
• Provide direct support to employees during implementation of
other administrative services, policies and programs
• Active participation in strategic planning process, including
developing goals, objectives and processes
• How to engage clients professionally
• Gain experience with Quickbook System and database
management and record keeping
*Note: You will have to pass and get the CEI (Basic) Certification before commencing work
